1390
02:17:40,009 --> 02:17:41,311
So it wasn't.

1391
02:17:42,052 --> 02:17:46,455
specifically tied to a particular version of the zoning ordinance.

1392
02:17:47,816 --> 02:17:56,941
And I think the rationale behind that is that it shows that the board has some flexibility in looking at these cases, excuse me, when

1393
02:17:58,762 --> 02:18:03,744
